Code : Interesting Alphabets
Send Feedback
Print the following pattern for the given number of rows.
Pattern for N = 5
E
DE
CDE
BCDE
ABCDE
Input format :
N (Total no. of rows)
Output format :
Pattern in N lines
Constraints
0 <= N <= 26
Sample Input 1:
8
Sample Output 1:
H
GH
FGH
EFGH
DEFGH
CDEFGH
BCDEFGH
ABCDEFGH
Sample Input 2:
7
Sample Output 2:
G
FG
EFG
DEFG
CDEFG
BCDEFG
ABCDEFG



solution:


#include<iostream>
using namespace std;


int main() {
  
    
  int i=1;
    int n;
    cin>>n;
    int num=n;
    while(i<=n){
        int j=1;
        char ch='A'+num-1;
        while(j<=i){
            cout<<ch;
            j++;
            ch++;
           
        }
        cout<<endl;
        num--;
        i++;
    }
    
}
